descriptionHtml:
Use all of your mimics with Mimic AI!

Mimic AI is the number 1 AI-powered reface & photo animating app that turns pictures into fun videos while using the latest artificial intelligence technologies. You can create limitless funny face video contents with our face swap feature. Mimic AI developed with an artificial intelligence algorithm that will protect the background of your videos. Mimic AI, combines deep fake technology with face swap and lip sync features. You can create funny faces, memes and bring your photos to life with this face swap feature easily. Replacing your face with any celebrity’s face in seconds or you can animate your childhood photo, experience nostalgia with your family and go back to the past in one click. It’s up to you! Because there are no limits to photo animating with Mimic AI! Get more interaction into your social media accounts. Engage with your friends and followers via Mimic AI! You can experience our magical deep fake technologies...


It’s simple to use Mimic AI:

1. Take on photo or choose a photo from your gallery
2. Pick a track from our large music collection
3. Generate any picture into funny deep fake video
4. Share a magical singing portrait with your friends or in your social media accounts (Tiktok, Instagram, Snapchat etc.).


Mimic AI Features:

• Listing content in GIF form
• Category-based listing (live, trendy, funny, celebrities,)
• Converting user-uploaded photo to video animation with selected music
• Searching feature
• Adding to favorites feature
• Capturing new photo or adding photos from the library


What do we offer with the Premium package?

• Access to Premium songs
• No advertisements
• Faster loading times
• Save and share high quality videos
• Removing watermark from videos

Why are you waiting? Reface your photos and generate deep fake funny videos.All you have to do is just download the app, take or choose a photo and watch yourself sing your heart out!
